    "posts": [
      {
        "media": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/geougc/AF1QipNU7IFixogfcOq3WQzMu67kh5svZiuO46qO6N8U=h400-no",
        "post_link": "https://search.google.com/local/posts?q=Village+Dental+Medicine&ludocid=15468172023206329628&lpsid=CIHM0ogKELrKjYmzsfDnfg&source=sh/x/loc/post&lsig=AB86z5UUPATyY5ucGhcTJrKNFMZJ",
        "description": "We understand that visiting the dentist can feel overwhelming for some people. That's why we've designed our practice with you in mind - spacious treatment rooms, a calming atmosphere, and a team that truly listens to your concerns.\n\nFrom the moment you walk in, you'll notice the difference. Our large terrace and soothing environment help you feel relaxed and at ease. We take the time to understand your needs and work with you to create a treatment plan that fits your life.\n\nAt Village Dental Medicine, we treat every person the way we'd want our own family members to be treated. Your comfort and care are always our top priorities.\n\n#DentalCare #PatientFirst #ComfortableDentistry #NewYorkDentist #QualityCare #DentalHealth",
        "date": "Jan 31, 2026"
      },
      {
        "media": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/geougc/AF1QipOqkw8fxZer5D8D3DsOCMvy8wOYf-xaBWLiYU3j=h400-no",
        "post_link": "https://search.google.com/local/posts?q=Village+Dental+Medicine&ludocid=15468172023206329628&lpsid=CIHM0ogKEJXJtunquqP63wE&source=sh/x/loc/post&lsig=AB86z5UUPATyY5ucGhcTJrKNFMZJ",
        "description": "Dental care doesn't have to be complicated or stressful. At Village Dental Medicine, we combine advanced technology with a gentle, straightforward approach that puts you at ease.\n\nWe know the dental world can seem full of confusing terms and procedures. That's why we speak in plain language and take time to answer your questions. Whether you're curious about digital x-rays, porcelain crowns, or periodontal treatment, we'll explain everything in a way that makes sense.\n\nOur state-of-the-art practice offers comprehensive services\u2014from preventive care to complete smile transformations\u2014all under one roof. You deserve dental care that's both excellent and accessible.\n\nWe believe in honest, transparent communication. No surprises, no pressure - just quality care delivered with genuine respect for you and your needs.\n\n#DentistryMadeSimple #ModernDental #TransparentCare #NewYorkDentistry #TrustedDentist #ComprehensiveCare #DentalExcellence",
        "date": "Jan 30, 2026"
      },
